          <p>
            Consider the following subsets of <m>\R^2</m> in the subspace topology:
            <me>
              A = \{ (x,y) \mid x^2+y^2 =1\} \ \ \ \text{ and }  \ \ \ B = \{ (x,0) \mid -1 \leq x \leq 1\}
            </me>.
